URL <- "http://static.lib.virginia.edu/statlab/materials/data/depression.csv"
dat <- read.csv(URL, stringsAsFactors = TRUE)
dat$id <- factor(dat$id)
dat$drug <- relevel(dat$drug, ref = "standard")
